snippet.title: TODAY
snippet.description: Wake up with TODAY! Start your day with the TODAY team on weekdays from 5.30am to 9am, and weekends from 7am, on the Nine Network, Australia. We hope you enjoy our channel, throughout 2018 and 2019 we'll be looking back at some of the most memorable moments of the TODAY Show years.
